text: Rodolfo Taguinod Albano III is a Filipino politician from Cabagan, Isabela, Philippines. He currently serves as the governor of Isabela. Albano was a congressman of the First Legislative District of Isabela from 2013 to 2019. ==References== ==External links== *Province of Isabela Official Website Category:Living people Category:Governors of Isabela (province) Category:PDP–Laban politicians Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Members of the House of Representatives of the Philippines from Isabela (province) Category:Ateneo de Manila University alumni Category:De La Salle University alumni
